          <div class="date">Feb 25, 2013</div>
				  <a href="/item/flag/19624299052_the_devil_in_silver?part_name=comment&amp;user_id=104240441" class="flagButton" id="flag_104240441_comment">Report This</a>            <div param="rate_316133024" class="ratingBlock">
    <ul class="starRating otherUserRating" title="not bad">
      <li class="currentRating" style="width: 30%">
        <span class="screen-reader-text">charlikitty rated this: 
        1.5 stars out of 5.</span></li>
